TradeGecko,is,an,online,inventory,and,order,management,platform,The,TradeGecko,API,provides,developer,access,to,that,platform,allowing,automated,manipulation,of,data,describing,customers,orders,inventory,and,more,The,API,communicates,over,HTTPS,and,authenticates,with,OAuth,HTTP,GET,PUT,POST,calls,are,supported,and,responses,are,JSON,format,The,API,also,supports,pagination,and,filtering,of,records